    "description": "<p>   INDECO ENGINEERS (PTE) LTD</p>  <p>    </p>  <table>   <tbody>         <td>      <p>       Established in 1983, Indeco is the first integrated facilities maintenance and management company in Singapore to undertake the facilities maintenance of Changi International Airport’s Terminal 1. Since then, the company has flourished by building on its core strengths and emerging as one of the top and most respected maintenance companies in Singapore.<br />       <br />       Today, Indeco, a wholly owned subsidairy of integrated logistics and supply chain management solutions provider CWT Group,provides a comprehensive range of maintenance and management services for buildings and other facilities, vehicles, equipment and container repairs. And with 700-strong trained workforce, Indeco has the right expertise to meet any challenges in facilities maintenance and management.<br />       <br />       The reputation we enjoy today is built on our core values of integrity, teamwork and excellence.<br />       <br />       Customers are our top priority. We believe in giving them nothing less than the best.</p>      <p>       Through Indeco, customers gain:</p>     </td>             <td>      <div>       •</div>     </td>     <td>      <div>       Optimum value and savings </div>     </td>             <td>      <div>       •</div>     </td>     <td>      Competitive edge </td>             <td>      <div>       •</div>     </td>     <td>      Increased flexibility</td>       </tbody>  </table>  <p>    </p>  ",
